title: Cake Masters - Full Year 2017 Collection
description:
Cake Masters - Full Year 2017 Collection
English | 12 issues | True PDF | 547 MB

Cake Masters Magazine is an exciting monthly cake and baking publication available in print and digitally. Each issue of the magazine is based on a theme and contains regular news, exclusive interviews, recipes, products, tutorials, special themed features and coverage of the best cake and baking shows from across the world. Cake Masters was born from the community of bakers and cake decorating enthusiasts who come together on ourpage to share creations and knowledge about all things baking. We are now a strong community of 650,000+ members baking, sharing and decorating – why not join us!
